data.description: Enjoy this 3 Bed/2 Bath w/ Garage on an oversized lot and lots of recent upgrades including Metal Roof (2019), New Backyard Screen Patio (2020) AC (2019) Stainless Appliances (2021) in the Updated Kitchen. Custom Closets in the bedrooms and a new front walkway are some of the nice surprises to the home . Enjoy relaxing mornings and evenings on your Screened Patio overlooking your green fenced backyard. Vaulted ceilings give the Living Room/Dining Room a roomy feel and get a great homeowners insurance discount for a newer roof and whole house hurricane shutters.
